xxl.core.indexStructures
Class BPlusTree.IndexEntry

java.lang.Object
  xxl.core.indexStructures.Tree.IndexEntry
      xxl.core.indexStructures.BPlusTree.IndexEntry
Enclosing class:
BPlusTree
public class BPlusTree.IndexEntry
extends Tree.IndexEntry

This class describes the index entries of the BPlusTree (i.e. the entries of the non-leaf nodes). Each IndexEntry refers to a Nodewhich is the root node of the subtree. Each IndexEntry has a Separator which describes the key range of this subtree.

See Also:
Tree.IndexEntry
